OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with further outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain in the morning across the
OL,7,Fwest, becoming drier through the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Dry in the east with some
OL,9,Fbright spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry, bright but
OL,12,Frather cloudy evening. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will remain dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells, especially in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FGood sunny spells between
OL,17,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,18,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,19,Fpassing shower possible in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
